Carol Kirkwood, 59, delighted BBC Breakfast viewers this morning when she presented the weather in a “beautiful” floral dress. The pink ensemble featured puffed sleeves and a flattering low-cut neckline. Many fans took to social media to compliment Carol on her wardrobe choice. John tweeted: “You are certainly looking refreshed and dazzling today.” Bradley praised: “You’re looking fabulous as ever.” Gary echoed: “You look great like you always do.” While Andy gushed: “Looking beautiful as ever.” And Keith raved: “Morning Carol you look beautiful, nice dress!” BBC Breakfast airs weekdays from 6am on BBC One.